        <mxCell id="6q5msQQIqbI2hkEbA6t--93" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#CBD5E1;fontColor=#232F3E;fontSize=12;align=left;spacing=8;" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;Controle no DynamoDB:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;• SOR_TABLE_CONFIG&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; Mapeia tabela de origem para tabela interna da SOR.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; Ex: db_origem.contrato → seguros_contratos&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;• PROCESS_RULES_CONFIG&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; Define quais tabelas SOR são necessárias para executar as regras do processo.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;• INGESTION_ID / HISTORY&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; Controla cada carga recebida e mantém o histórico das versões carregadas.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;• CURRENT_SOR&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; Aponta a última versão válida de cada tabela SOR por processo.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;• PROCESS / PROCESS_LIST&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; Controla a execução das regras de negócio e permite listar execuções por processo/data_referencia.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;• INPUT_LOCK&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; Congela quais ingestion_id serão usados em um process_id.&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
